You can now add hints to Hookshot messages to disable URL previews on clients. Uses [MSC4095](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/4095).

See https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-hookshot/latest/setup.html#messaging-defaults and https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-hookshot/latest/setup/webhooks.html#v2-api
